 Guizhi Fuling Wan on intestinal flora (in G group, the relative abundance ofAlloprevotella, Ruminococcaceae UCG-003, andLachnospiraceae UCG-008was increased significantly, compared with M group). This research demonstrates Guizhi Fuling Wan improve insulin resistance in polycystic ovary syndrome with the underlying mechanism of regulating intestinal flora to control inflammation. It would be useful to promote the therapeutic effect of Guizhi Fuling Wan on PCOS-IR.
