   Conclusion: The ACTION ICU score may be a promising tool to identify the need for ICU care in Latin-American patients with NSTEMI. Furthermore, additional research is needed to evaluate the cost-effectiveness of this strategy. (C) 2022 The Author( s). Published by Elsevier Inc.
